text: Rochelle Eulah Eileen Humes (n√©e Wiseman; born 21 March 1989) is a British pop singer and actress. She was born in Barking, London to a British mother and Sierra Leonean father. She was a member of S Club 8. Since 2007, she is a member of girl group The Saturdays. She is married to Marvin Humes of JLS.
